{"id": "1444886130540548231", "channel_id": "1444886130540548231", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "Would it be possible to request an additional version of OST1, Track 9, to be available in-game, without the first 10 seconds? The goal would be to use it as a BGM track for the lobby. Right now, using this track as BGM will play the initial fanfare every time, and it takes a while to wait for the main song to start playing.\n\nThis track: https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1229391410453680138/1229392905551085618\n\nThe first 10 seconds of the song is very distinct and separate from the main song track, so I would like to suggest that a different version of the song to be added without that first 10 seconds. This way, the track can be used for BGM in the lobby much more effectively.", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T03:01:38.207000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-01T03:02:49.109000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "shy", "emoji_id": "1356053151349997829", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1444886131366690817", "filename": "9.-To_be_Continued-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 22012766, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444886130540548231/1444886131366690817/9.-To_be_Continued-.wav?ex=69fb57d2&is=69fa0652&hm=8466dd9017a2e1ecc517bfd974915cf7cc9c5d255d244e287ee6c0b4a3612de5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1444886130540548231", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Standalone version of OST1 Track9 for BGM use", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
