{"id": "1444977668654104586", "channel_id": "1444977668654104586", "type": 0, "author_id": "1001696859225591869", "author_name": "o5214658", "author_bot": false, "content": "喵了個咪的！\n之前說難度調低缺乏挑戰性，後來難度又調回來了。\n結果根本不是調回來，而是全面加強難度了啊！\n基本上現行所有不吃靈知的打法，都要依靠繁育刻印的爆牌輔助，不然那個見鬼的大眼睛高傷高血多階段是要怎麼打啊！\n難度調回來是沒啥意見，但還提高了這就不能忍了！！！<:angry1:1356053023272599668>", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T09:05:22.594000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "A_pinch", "emoji_id": "1432980538536493057", "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1444977668654104586", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "繁育刻印廢了？！", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1444934387782258780", "channel_id": "1444934387782258780", "type": 0, "author_id": "126439705934954497", "author_name": "sephallia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I was able to clear the raid fine with another party (Caecus, Ogier, Tawil, borrow Nautila) but when running the party in the screenshot, the boss got stuck after clearing. There are a lot of bonuses for using Posse, so I'm wondering if it might be Ramona Timeworn?", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T06:13:23.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1444934388113604790", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2605452, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444934387782258780/1444934388113604790/image.png?ex=6a00cac3&is=69ff7943&hm=c620fcdc5feee5af9d0f4212c50acb44b20d083dd8b041c68dbf383318edb2d0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1444934387782258780", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Raid stuck after clearing fight seemingly only on certain parties?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1445118990262341843", "channel_id": "1445118990262341843", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "In the previous patch notes this entry was present:\n> We further optimized the story text display to enhance the reading experience. Multi-line story text now appears faster and remains on screen for sufficient reading time before scrolling up. Scrolling is now controlled manually and will not automatically happen (unless autoplay is turned on). Additionally, the text size was adjusted to display more content at once.\nBut in the current story, where there is a long line, like in Arc2 Chapter 2-15 or ch 6-15 or any other, you can't scroll manually and the speed seems the same as before.\nWas that fix a lie? was it removed after the last patch by mistake? or is not even for the Main Story Dialogue Text?", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T18:26:56.291000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445118990547550268", "filename": "imdfgfgfgage.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 39633, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445118990262341843/1445118990547550268/imdfgfgfgage.png?ex=6a00cdf0&is=69ff7c70&hm=597e160f7c68b38afb473f672cb3bf70c85ecd4c45b561ef1b590668ee46ae67&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445118990262341843", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Auto-scroll fixes not in effect", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1445108630197375170", "channel_id": "1445108630197375170", "type": 0, "author_id": "105236306337996800", "author_name": "meioh", "author_bot": false, "content": "Why does Doresain not create a Evernight Revel when gaining a corpse through his own posse?", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T17:45:46.259000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445108630654419047", "filename": "IMG_3266.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1022646, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445108630197375170/1445108630654419047/IMG_3266.png?ex=6a00c44a&is=69ff72ca&hm=fcbb40831b8f4e2ca89d9fa2eed495ab99c5e7aefcb90d5c9f896e8d6eba3efa&"}, {"id": "1445108631157608591", "filename": "IMG_3267.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1209425, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445108630197375170/1445108631157608591/IMG_3267.png?ex=6a00c44a&is=69ff72ca&hm=ffc1576906821103d5e4df789a98c09e38fe6bba416ed71ba937018db44eb6bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445108630197375170", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Cruel homage posse bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1445154383858761881", "channel_id": "1445154383858761881", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "This is a post that will be updated with everyone opinions on what are the most relevant problems and most effective solutions, to then push the feedback directly to Light, free to share yours opinions and argument it below.\n\n**Problems:**\n\n- **1) **Limited quantity of clears before the stage is removed (unfair for different time zones and can exclude a big number of the growing community, making the event feel more competitive than collaborative);\n- **2) **Too many runs per Stage to get the maximum number of Rewards (even if completing all the clears is not mandatory, for who can even do it, the feeling of loosing on precious materials is grading, and so people may feel pressured to complete all the clears they can and burn out on the game);\n- **3)** Necessity of using a Support on every stage (this is a minor annoyance and possibly mitigated if we reduce the total clears needed).\n\n**Possible Solutions:**\n\n- **1)** Make so each boss has a **Community Goal** that will be reached after a certain number of combined clears with the help of all the players, giving a rewards to everyone that did 1 clear in it, even after the goal is reached (the stage will not be closed after the goal is set, so that people can still complete the 5 clears listed below, so the event will instead have a Set Duration, like a month);\n- **2) ** **Condense the Rewards** per run, so you get more for the first clear, and a bit less on each subsequent one in the same stage (with a possible cap for the silver and rare material at the 5th, or around that, with additional clears giving only exp and counting for the Total Community Goal).", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T20:47:34.782000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 17}, {"emoji": "THIS", "emoji_id": "1181043334056259695", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1445154384387510282", "filename": "sdfg.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 225730, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445154383858761881/1445154384387510282/sdfg.JPG?ex=6a004626&is=69fef4a6&hm=0156ec509c007496bc091582eb339c295f7215efe7663941729a3f173681a00b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445154383858761881", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Raid Problems and Solutions (The feedbacks have been shared with Light )", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
